name: In love with my body
description:
This piece was born out of re-connection, observance, and love for my body.

I am in awe and appreciation of how each an every cell of my body works to keep me together, healthy, and beautiful. And now I witness their creation in the mirror and finally see myself for how beautiful I am. How beautiful each one of us are.

Each of our varied skins, sizes, types, hair, muscles, and movements are beautiful to witness.

And this piece is in celebration of that appreciation. The grace by which we are alive and can witness the world.
